title: 5 meter Alaska Digital Elevation Models (DEMs) - USGS National Map
name: 5-meter-alaska-digital-elevation-models-dems-usgs-national-map
notes: This dataset is comprised of 5-meter ifsar-derived Digital Elevation Models (DEMs) over Alaska only. It is distributed as one-degree blocks with overedge.
